This update brings Beloved Features and NEW unique experiences you ve never had before in such an app: ALTERNATIVE ICONS: Personalize Swiftgram your way with five stylish icons. QUICK TRANSLATE BUTTON: Translate messages with a single tap. OUTGOING TRANSLATION: Long tap the Send button to translate your text into chat language. FOLDERS AT BOTTOM: Easy access to the folders panel. SAVE TO CLOUD: Instantly forward any message to your Favourites. DATACENTER INFO: Apart from Profile IDs you can now view the DC. Unique Features you ve never seen before: IMPROVED LOCAL SEARCH: Search messages in Chinese Korean Japanese and other languages. Even with one character! UPLOADS BOOST: Share the media up to 10 times faster. SMALL REACTIONS: Reduce visual noise and flatten the reactions to focus on the content. By the way there were some bug fixes improvements and an update to Telegram s 10.4 source code. Stay updated with swiftgram and join a discussion at swiftgramchat!
